+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HsYdiatRPyQzNZCH9UqE9W","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Phase 7: Task Dependencies\n     2→\n     3→Add the ability for tasks to declare dependencies on other tasks, so they only become available once their prerequisites are done.\n     4→\n     5→## Requirements\n     6→\n     7→- When adding a task, you can specify a list of task IDs that must complete before this task becomes available.\n     8→- A task with unresolved dependencies is blocked and will not be returned when retrieving.\n     9→- When a dependency completes, the system should check whether any blocked tasks are now unblocked.\n    10→- Circular dependencies (direct or indirect) must be detected and rejected at task-creation time.\n    11→- Depending on a non-existent task should cause an error.\n    12→- A failed dependency does NOT automatically fail its dependents -- they remain blocked.\n    13→- There should be a way to inspect a task's dependency status.\n    14→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2107b12e-f12a-4d0c-bc47-bb3ab39302b3","uuid":"775d5268-62bd-45c0-9810-f3f99fcd82ab","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/phases/phase-07.md","content":"# Phase 7: Task Dependencies\n\nAdd the ability for tasks to declare dependencies on other tasks, so they only become available once their prerequisites are done.\n\n## Requirements\n\n- When adding a task, you can specify a list of task IDs that must complete before this task becomes available.\n- A task with unresolved dependencies is blocked and will not be returned when retrieving.\n- When a dependency completes, the system should check whether any blocked tasks are now unblocked.\n- Circular dependencies (direct or indirect) must be detected and rejected at task-creation time.\n- Depending on a non-existent task should cause an error.\n- A failed dependency does NOT automatically fail its dependents -- they remain blocked.\n- There should be a way to inspect a task's dependency status.\n","numLines":14,"startLine":1,"totalLines":14}}}
